rows.label: tev036701_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Wersal about Ma-non clothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0001
rows.name:
As thin and light as our clothes are, they are still
exceedingly durable, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0002
rows.name:
But they're not anywhere near as interesting as your
Earth fashion, right? They don't make a a a statement,
I suppose you might say.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0003
rows.name:
That's why I've been dying to to try on Alesa's clothes.
I don't care if they're fit for space travel—just browsing
the store racks makes me happy, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0008
rows.name:
Normally, we Ma-non don't fuss over how we
look, you see? So I guess the only one of us who
really understands my love for fashion is is Panyar?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0009
rows.name:
You haven't met her? Oh. Maybe you need to get
around more?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0010
rows.name:
Panyar has been to just about every clothing store
in the city, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0011
rows.name:
She said she was going to develop a clothing line just
for Ma-non, so I hope that's still in the works?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0020
rows.name:
If I designed ground gear for humans, I'd probably use
the thinnest, most transparent fabric I could and cover
up only what I had to, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0021
rows.name: ...What's that? You'd be practically naked?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0022
rows.name:
Er, does that even matter? I mean, it's it's not like
you're displaying your real body, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0023
rows.name:
Sometimes you humans just don't make any sense
at all, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0033
rows.name:
I guess you heard? Panyar's attempt at at designing
unmentionables was a royal bust...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0034
rows.name:
I considering buying some, but Alesa said to stay
clear, so I passed. That was probably the right choice,
don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0035
rows.name:
However, this perfume Panyar came up with instead is
a real winner, right? It smells so so so nice![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036701_MSG0038
rows.name:
She'll always be a pioneer to me. I mean, where would
Ma-non fashion be without her? Nowhere, am I right?[ST:wait ]
